descriptionNullable:
This dataset is a compilation of various medical image datasets available on Kaggle.

Currently it contains data for the following
- Kidney Cancer
- Cervical Cancer
- Alzheimer's
- Covid 19
- Pneumonia
- Tuberculosis
- Monkeypox
- Malaria

and for preprocessing Chest X-Ray
- Bone Shadow Suppression Dataset
title: Medical Scan Classification Dataset
subtitle: Image dataset of various diseases
